Title: DataSense Ai
Short Description: Smart AI analytics for every dataset
Content:
Project Overview

DataSense AI is an AI-powered business intelligence platform designed to transform raw datasets into actionable insights within minutes. Users can securely upload CSV files, after which the system performs intelligent preprocessing — including privacy-sensitive data removal, normalization, and feature enhancement. Once cleaned, the processed dataset is automatically uploaded to Supabase for secure storage, and users can seamlessly visualize insights through tools like Tableau and Power BI. Due to NDA constraints, the actual project name and UI images cannot be disclosed.

Key Features

  • AI-driven data preprocessing (auto-cleaning, privacy filtering, normalization)
  • Automated upload to Supabase for secure, scalable storage
  • Seamless integration with Tableau and Power BI for advanced analytics
  • KPI Layer Generator — AI automatically creates dashboards and insight-rich views
  • AI conversational analytics bot for natural-language querying of datasets
  • Automated anomaly detection and intelligent recommendations
  • End-to-end data pipeline with strong privacy and enterprise-grade scalability

Technologies Used

The platform is built using Next.js, Node.js, Supabase, and OpenAI's API for preprocessing, insight generation, and conversational analytics. It supports large dataset uploads, ensures strict privacy handling, and delivers fast, AI-powered KPI dashboards and chatbot-driven insights.

Title: Song Ai
Content:
Project Overview

Song AI is an AI-powered songwriting assistant designed to help creators generate full songs, including lyrics, melodies, and structured verses, in minutes. Users can input themes, moods, or keywords, after which the system performs intelligent song generation — including rhyme optimization, melody suggestions, and verse-chorus structuring. The generated songs can be saved, exported, or refined further using the platform's AI tools. Due to NDA constraints, the actual project name and UI images cannot be disclosed.

Key Features

  • AI-powered lyric generation based on themes, moods, and keywords
  • Automatic verse, chorus, and bridge structuring for complete songs
  • Rhyme and rhythm optimization for catchy, natural lyrics
  • Melody suggestions and chord progression guidance
  • Interactive AI refinement for edits and creative inspiration
  • Export options for text, sheet music, or DAW-ready formats
  • End-to-end songwriting workflow with fast, AI-assisted creativity

Technologies Used

The platform is built using Next.js, Node.js, Supabase, and OpenAI's API for lyric generation, melody assistance, and interactive refinement. It supports secure storage of user creations, fast AI-powered song generation, and intuitive tools for writers of all skill levels.

Title: FixMate
Short Description: Smart solutions for faster repairs and tracking.
Content:
Project Overview

FixMate is a comprehensive platform designed to streamline service requests and maintenance management for businesses and households. Users can easily log repair requests, track technician assignments, and receive real-time updates. The system intelligently prioritizes tasks, manages schedules, and ensures seamless communication between clients and service providers. Due to NDA constraints, the actual project name and UI images cannot be disclosed.

Key Features

  • Service request logging with real-time updates
  • Intelligent task prioritization and scheduling
  • Technician assignment and tracking system
  • In-app communication between clients and service providers
  • Automated reminders and follow-ups for pending tasks
  • Detailed reporting and analytics for service performance
  • Secure, end-to-end workflow management for maintenance operations

Technologies Used

The platform is built using Next.js, Node.js, Supabase, and Firebase for real-time updates and secure storage. It integrates notification systems, analytics dashboards, and robust workflow management tools to ensure efficient service delivery and client satisfaction.

Title: Golden Events
Short Description: Personal finance management dashboard with investment tracking
Content:
Project Overview

GoldenEvents is a user-friendly event booking platform designed specifically for elderly users, making it easy to discover, register, and attend community events. The platform provides an intuitive interface with large fonts, simple navigation, and voice-assisted features. Users can browse events by category, date, or location, receive reminders, and get real-time updates about their registrations. Due to NDA constraints, the actual project name and UI images cannot be disclosed.

Key Features

  • Intuitive, senior-friendly interface with large fonts and clear navigation
  • Event discovery by category, date, or location
  • Simple registration and booking process for events
  • Voice-assisted navigation and accessibility features
  • Automated reminders and notifications for upcoming events
  • Real-time updates on event changes or cancellations
  • Secure storage of user profiles and booking history

Technologies Used

The platform is built using React Native, Node.js, Supabase, and Firebase for real-time notifications. It supports accessibility features, secure storage of user data, and seamless event management to ensure a hassle-free experience for elderly users.

Title: Grocery E-commerce Platform
Short Description: Smart UI for hassle-free grocery shopping
Content:
Project Overview

A user-friendly e-commerce platform for grocery shopping, designed to simplify the online grocery experience. Features include intuitive product browsing, smart search and filters, seamless checkout, and personalized recommendations. The UI is optimized for mobile and desktop, providing a fast and enjoyable shopping experience.

Key Features

  • Intuitive navigation and product categorization
  • Smart search and filter options
  • Personalized product recommendations
  • Smooth, multi-step checkout
  • Mobile-responsive design

Technologies Used

Figma, Adobe XD, React, Next.js

One-Line: Smart UI for hassle-free grocery shopping

Title: Electrical Shop E-commerce Platform
Content:
Project Overview

A modern e-commerce solution for electrical shops, focusing on easy browsing, product comparison, and quick checkout. Designed with user experience in mind, it helps customers find products quickly while providing clear information, pricing, and stock availability. Mobile-friendly and visually engaging for higher conversions.

Key Features

  • Easy product browsing and comparison
  • Detailed product information and specs
  • Quick and secure checkout process
  • Mobile-optimized responsive design
  • Promotional banners and offers integration

Technologies Used

Figma, Adobe XD, React, Next.js

One-Line: Effortless shopping for electrical products
